## Configuration

### Environment Variables

```bash
# Service
SERVICE_NAME={{ service_name | upper }}
SERVICE_PORT={{ port }}
NODE_ENV=development

{% if database %}
# Database
DATABASE_URL={{ database | upper }}_URL
DATABASE_POOL_SIZE=10
{% endif %}

{% if cache %}
# Cache
CACHE_URL={{ cache | upper }}_URL
CACHE_TTL=3600
{% endif %}

# Monitoring
OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_ENDPOINT=http://otel-collector:4317
```

### Configuration File

`config/config.yaml`:
```yaml
service:
  name: {{ service_name }}
  port: {{ port }}
  protocol: {{ protocol | lower }}

{% if database %}
database:
  type: {{ database | lower }}
  host: localhost
  port: 5432
  database: {{ service_name | lower }}
  pool_size: 10
{% endif %}

{% if cache %}
cache:
  type: {{ cache | lower }}
  host: localhost
  port: 6379
  ttl: 3600
{% endif %}

monitoring:
  enabled: true
  traces_exporter: otlp
  metrics_exporter: prometheus
```

